{"id":"hebron-2","term":"Hebron (2)","source":"International Standard Bible Encyclopaedia (James Orr ed., 1915)","html":"<p>(chebhron, \"league,\" \"association\"):</p><p>(1) The third son of Kohath, son of Levi (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Exodus 6:18\">Ex 6:18</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 3:19\">Nu 3:19</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 3:27\">27</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 6:2\">1Ch 6:2</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 6:18\">18</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 23:12\">23:12</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 23:19\">19</a>).</p><p>(2) A son of Mareshah and descendant of Caleb (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 2:42\">1Ch 2:42</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 2:43\">43</a>).</p><p>See also KORAH.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Exodus 6:18","Numbers 3:19","Numbers 3:27","1 Chronicles 6:2","1 Chronicles 6:18","1 Chronicles 23:12","1 Chronicles 23:19","1 Chronicles 2:42","1 Chronicles 2:43"]}